name: Custom Case
description:
Custom cases range from $45-60 depending on the design.Case cost is included in price.

1. Before buying, please let me know what type of phone you have and the colors you want and I will give you the price.Please contact me at hunniebunn16@yahoo.com

2. 50% NON-REFUNDABLE DEPOSIT IS REQUIRED.I won't start to work on the order until deposit is received. This deposit is NOT refundable.I had some customers in the past that requested a custom item but didn't buy it after the item was made.I spend hours to decorate each and every case.I will send you a paypal invoice for the deposit whenever you are ready. Please provide me with your email address.

3. It usually takes 3-5 business days for the case to come in and another 1-3 days for the case to be decorated and ready to be shipped. It may take longer if I have high volume of orders

4. Once the case is made, I will send you an email with pictures so you can check out how it came out. Paypal invoice for the remaining balance will be also sent

If you want to see more cases I've done, check out my instagram @theefkngoddess :) 

Thank you!
